_comment: Manual overrides for known data quality issues in source APIs. Each entry describes a venue with incorrect coordinates that should be dropped. These are auto-detected by borough bounding box validation but listed here explicitly so the corrections are transparent and auditable. If you are adapting this project for a different region, you can safely delete this file or replace it with your own overrides -- the build will still run the bbox validation automatically.
